*********************************** 
counter strike source map file
*********************************** 
TITLE: gg_escher
AUTHOR: boddah 
E-MAIL: tyson_sumner@hotmail.com 
 
FILENAME: gg_escher.bsp, also the following .txt, .vmt, and .vtf for radar overview. 
 
DATE RELEASED: March 2007 

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: put the .bsp file in \steamapps\XXXXXXXXX\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps.  

                           put the .txt file in  \steamapps\XXXXXXXX\counter-strike source\cstrike\resource\overviews

                           and put the .vtf anf .vmt files in steamapps\XXXXXx\counter-strike source\cstrike\materials\overviews 

                           and you're done.

DESCRIPTION: a counter strike gun game map that uses simple dev textures. nothing new or fancy.

BUGS: ive been told that the radar is overly green. there are also no buy zones because it is meant for gun game servers.

COMMENTS: hope you all enjoy.
